ValidateBuildResponse
/ Validates the LLM build response
- if %response.steps.Count% is not %goal.Steps.Count%, throw error 'LLM returned %response.steps.Count% steps but goal has %goal.Steps.Count% steps. Steps are lines starting with '- '. Return exactly one result per goal step.'
- foreach %response.steps%, call ValidateStep, item=%step%

ValidateStep
/ Validates a single step from the LLM response
- if %step.actions% is empty
    - throw error 'Step at index %step.index% has no actions. Every step must include actions with module and action filled in.'
